snippet.title: LAST STOP | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to Xbox and PC. Wishlist here: https://annapurna.link/LastStop

From Variable State, the award-winning creators of VIRGINIA, comes LAST STOP. A single-player third-person adventure set in present day London, you play as three separate characters whose worlds collide in the midst of a supernatural crisis. 

An anthology drama, LAST STOP is three stories in one. What connects these three strangers? Where will fate lead them?

Developed by VARIABLE STATE. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2019
